<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Your privacy is important to us. We are committed to protecting your personal data and being transparent about how we handle it.</p>

    <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>We collect personal information (e.g., name, email) and usage data (e.g., IP address, cookies) for the purpose of improving our services and communicating with you.</p>

    <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
    <p>We use your data to provide and improve our services, send updates, and ensure security.</p>

    <h3>3. Data Sharing</h3>
    <p>We do not share your data with third parties, except when necessary to comply with legal obligations or with your consent.</p>

    <h3>4. Data Retention</h3>
    <p>We keep your data only as long as necessary and delete it upon request.</p>

    <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. To do so, contact us at any time.</p>

    <h3>6. Security</h3>
    <p>We use reasonable measures to protect your data, but no method is 100% secure.</p>

    <h3>7. Updates to This Policy</h3>
    <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>

</div>

